{"tid":1118000,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時開始知道自己咁虧","createTime":"2019-04-21T05:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T08:01:38.000Z","uid":192551,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2930b31c4a264a0b7a8903188be356719498bce4","tid":1118000,"uid":192551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"一上大學發覺身邊啲人通宵做project，自己捱唔到夜，一過12點就勁眼瞓，一遲過2點瞓第日個人又頭暈又冇精神。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細細個腸胃都好撚差，幾乎日日痛，但細個抖下又冇野，冇理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。到依家有時痛撚到行街就暈撚左，痾緊屎個心跳到勁快，抖唔氣，諗緊會唔會隨時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞到依家好鬼養生，咩夜瞓，凍飲要戒，仲要晚晚浸下腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時會諗點解人地出面玩緊既時我係屋企做緊阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs.先廿幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028f7bfcfeb7dd1973b318376e3b96d5bc3a0bb4","tid":1118000,"uid":186844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"由細到大都通頂唔到 一定會訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5a849d95c3b6e35601e2a109511e38dd144db8","tid":1118000,"uid":128974,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"練下就OK<br />\n每個星期晏1個鐘瞓<br />\n一個月之後 每日就可以練到多4個鐘用"},{"pid":"59376bb9ae569ad0ca8cd11482d2c5a460d29161","tid":1118000,"uid":192551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"028f7bfcfeb7dd1973b318376e3b96d5bc3a0bb4","tid":1118000,"uid":186844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"由細到大都通頂唔到 一定會訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:08:43.000Z","msg":"有個frd又係咩環境都好瞓上床5分鐘入睡，好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d96e4aa884d4d44a5967db3dbb737993018cb59","tid":1118000,"uid":18569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"永遠10點半就上床瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話知你個日好撚忙好多野做又點都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔飲得凍野，一飲就係咁咳喉嚨又唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757a8a0821f4b440c741cd7c895a4d1081550b77","tid":1118000,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"差勁"},{"pid":"9739e8b72e2af45675da918f8ea492e71d14f3cc","tid":1118000,"uid":192551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"757a8a0821f4b440c741cd7c895a4d1081550b77","tid":1118000,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"差勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a83bdcda3c54024ad60a4dea6ec7e503b0269f4","tid":1118000,"uid":192551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d96e4aa884d4d44a5967db3dbb737993018cb59","tid":1118000,"uid":18569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"永遠10點半就上床瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話知你個日好撚忙好多野做又點都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔飲得凍野，一飲就係咁咳喉嚨又唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:22:57.000Z","msg":"屌你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdec9b7be190c2ce28d66a1487e1e243b7fcce5","tid":1118000,"uid":192551,"li